--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a49675d3da19b054686ae9ecd58461ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: SecondInteractionShop
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "\u2026You again."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1a1f0c89fd2ad8f488fa25619df9f084, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: Let me guess. Forest chewed you up and spat you back out.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: Tha's not cool cutie!... but yeah something like that the energy from this
      planet change the time and space.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "Astraeon\u2019s energy likes to recycle rookies. Don\u2019t get too proud
      about it."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19b79383905171c41b80cd4bec17b504, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: You fall, the planet drags you back to where you started. Happens to outsiders
      all the time.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c048e118567af15419bcdcc777d7bf53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 582011cdf7050c44f8084097286d9f66, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: At least it gives me another chance.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19b79383905171c41b80cd4bec17b504, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: Yeah, yeah. Just try not to make a habit of it.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1a1f0c89fd2ad8f488fa25619df9f084, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "Every time you pop back in, the wildlife gets jumpy. And I don\u2019t
      feel like dealing with extra trouble because you decided to take a nap in the
      dirt."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19b79383905171c41b80cd4bec17b504, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: "I\u2019ll keep that in mind."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7dd5bd74fab0f024d8b7d28ff2d45b8c, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: Good. Now move and bring me some money rookie!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  options: []
  isFinalDialogue: 0
